{"id":542550,"date":[{"year":1975,"month":3,"day":2}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"风雷激","column":"","genre":"","count":"66","ytitle":"","mtitle":"农场天地广","ftitle":"","authors":["谈佩华"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄山茶林场二连　谈佩华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农场天地广，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美景我梳妆；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立下务农志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎着风浪闯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扎根在山乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为党争荣光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终身不回头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"办好茶林场。"}]}